## 🧠 About Me
Designer × AI Explorer × Independent Researcher

I am exploring:
- ✦ Autonomous learning systems
- ✦ Knowledge formation
- ✦ Self-correction mechanisms
- ✦ Curiosity-driven exploration
- ✦ Cognitive architectures

### 🌠 AsteriaMind
> "Not only learning answers,
> but learning how to learn."

AsteriaMind is an experimental AI architecture focused on this core loop:

Experience
    ↓
Learning
    ↓
Hypothesis
    ↓
Verification
    ↓
Knowledge
    ↓
Self-improvement


### 🧬 Architecture Evolution

HiveMind v0.x
Multiple agents
Energy competition
Fixed biases

        ↓

HiveMind v2.0
Learned biases
Argument evaluation
Adaptive trust

        ↓

AsteriaMind
Curiosity Engine
Knowledge Core
Skill Evolution
World Model


